aj]]\n|-\n!''[[Pandurangadu]]''\n|\"Prema Valambanam\"\n|[[M. M. Keeravani]]\n|-\n![[Vandemataram Srinivas|''Maha Yagnam'']]\n|\"Ayyo Idhi Amanusham\"\n|[[Vandemataram Srinivas]]\n|-\n!''[[Durai (film)|Gajendra]]''\n|\"Challani Punnami\"\n|[[D. Imman]]\n|-\n!''[[Maa Ayana Chanti Pilladu]]''\n|\"Emandoy Sreevaru\"\n|[[M. M. Srilekha]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" |2009\n! rowspan=\"2\" |[[Ajantha (2012 film)|''Ajantha'']]\n|\"Raave Swarama\"(Version l)\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Ilaiyaraaja]]\n|-\n|\"Raave Swarama\"(Version ll)\n|-\n!''[[Aa Okkadu]]''\n|\"Vuruko Manasa\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|-\n!''[[Taj Mahal]]''\n|\"Chellani Premaku\"\n|[[M. M. Srilekha]]\n|-\n!''[[Raju Maharaju]]''\n|\"Mamatala Kovela\"\n|[[Chakri (composer)|Chakri]]\n|-\n![[Vidyasagar (composer)|Joy]]\n|\"Megham Madhuram\"\n|[[Vidhya Sagar]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" |2010\n!''[[Kalyanram Kathi|Kalayanram Kathi]]''\n|\"Jai Jai Ram\"\n|[[Mani Sharma]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" |[[Aayirathil Oruvan (2010 film)|''Yuganiki Okkadu'']]\n|\"Singarinchina\"\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[G. V. Prakash Kumar]]\n|-\n|\"Daachindi Manne\"\n|-\n|\"Mammalni Paalinchi\"\n|-\n!''[[Lava Kusa: The Warrior Twins]]''\n|\"Niliche Sathyam\"\n|[[L. Vaidyanathan]]\n|-\n![[1977 (film)|''1977'']]\n|\"Oke Oka\"\n|[[Vidhya Sagar]]\n|-\n![[Kanimozhi (film)|''Love Journey'']]\n|\"Punnami Punnami\"\n|[[Satish Chakravarthy]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2013\n![[Kadal (2013 film)|''Kadali'']]\n|\"Chitti Jaabili\"\n|[[A. R. Rahman]]\n|-\n!''[[Dalam]]''\n|\"Yetellina\"\n|[[James Vasanthan]]\n|-\n!''[[Vijay Yesudas|Yedalo]]''\n|\"Raagam Yedaina\"\n|Jagadish Pamarthi\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2014\n![[Legend (2014 film)|''Legend'']]\n|\"Nee Kanti Choopulloki\"\n|[[Devi Sri Prasad]]\n|-\n!''[[Govindudu Andarivadele]]''\n|\"Bavagari Choope\"\n|[[Yuvan Shankar Raja]]\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Erra Bus]]''\n|\"Ontariga Nuvvunte\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Chakri (composer)|Chakri]]\n|-\n|\"Aakashana\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2015\n! rowspan=\"2\" |[[Tommy (2015 film)|''Tommy'']]\n|\"Aakasham Pampinda\"\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Chakri (composer)|Chakri]]\n|-\n|\"Nuvve Kanipinchaka\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2016\n!''[[Kalyana Vaibhogame]]''\n|\"Evaru Neevu\"\n|[[Kalyani Malik]]\n|-\n![[Pulimurugan|''Manyam Puli'']]\n|\"Muvvalane Navvinche\"\n|[[Gopi Sundar]]\n|-\n!''[[Oka Manasu]]''\n|\"Hrudayama Kalusuko\"\n|[[Sunil Kashyap]]\n|-\n!''[[Premam]]''\n|\"Evare\"\n|[[Rajesh Murugesan]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2017\n!''[[Shatamanam Bhavati]]''\n|\"Shatamanam Bhavathi\"\n|[[Mickey J. Meyer]]\n|-\n!''[[List of Telugu films of 2017|Sriramudinta Srikrishnudanta]]''\n|\"Adugutho Aduge\"\n|Naresh Penta\n|-\n!''[[Kaadhali (2017 film)|Kaadhali]]''\n|\"Nuvvante Nenani\"\n| Prasan Praveen Shyam\n|-\n!''[[Nene Raju Nene Mantri]]''\n|\"Radhamma Radhamma\"\n|[[Anup Rubens]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" |2018\n!''[[Jai Simha]]''\n|\"Anaganaga Anaganaga\"\n|[[Chirantan Bhatt]]\n|-\n!''[[Nela Ticket]]''\n|\"Chuttu Janam\"\n|Shaktikanth Karthik\n|-\n!''[[Shailaja Reddy Alludu]]''\n|\"Pelli Pandiri\"\n|[[Gopi Sundar]]\n|-\n!''[[Bhairava Geetha]]''\n|\"Bhagavad Geetha\"\n|Ravi Shankar\n|-\n![[List of Telugu films of 2018|''Ala'']]\n|\"Ala Loni\"\n|Srinivas Sharma Rani\n|-\n![[List of Telugu films of 2018|''Sathya Gang'']]\n|\"Yevaru Chesina Papam\" \n|Prabhas\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" |2019\n!''[[Guna 369]]''\n|\"Manasukidi Garalam\"\n|Chaitanya Bharadwaj\n|-\n!''[[Tholu Bommalata]]''\n|\"Goppadira Manishi\"\n|Suresh Bobbili\n|-\n!''[[Aswamedham]]''\n|\"Ganesha\"\n|Charan Arjun\n|-\n!''[[Prati Roju Pandage]]''\n|\"Chinnataname\"\n|[[S. Thaman]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2020\n!''[[Sunil Kashyap|Degree College]]''\n|\"Neeve Neeve\"\n|[[Sunil Kashyap]]\n|-\n!''Oka Chinna Viramam''\n|\"Yeduruga Ranamunna\"\n|Bharath Manchiraju\n|-\n!''Uma Maheswara Ugra Roopasy''\n|\"Ningi Chutte\"\n|[[Bijibal]]\n|}\n\n==Malayalam discography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n!Film\n! Songs\n!Composer\n|-\n| 2012\n! Spirit\n|\"Mazhakondu Mathram\" \n|Shabaz aman\n|-\n| 2019\n! Rakshapurushan\n|\"Parayu Engu Nee\" \n| Jibin George Sebastian\n|-\n| 2019\n! Vijay Superum Pournamiyum\n|\"Etho Mazhayil\" , \"Pakalaay\"\n| Prince George\n|} \n<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news24hours.in/2019/05/10/from-hollywood-to-mollywood-jibin-george-sebastian-has-composed-2-songs-for-the-upcoming-movie-rakshapurushan/|title=From Hollywood to Mollywood|work=News24hours}}</ref>\n\n==Tamil discography==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n!Film\n! Songs\n!Composer\n|-\n| 2020\n! ''[[Kanni Maadam]]'' \n|\"Oru Veedu\"  || Hari Sai\n|}\n\n==Filmography==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Film\n! Role\n! Director\n!Language\n|-\n|2010\n|''[[Avan (2010 film)|Avan]]''\n| Apu \n| Nandan Kavil\n|[[Malayalam]]\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Maari (film)|Maari]]''\n| Arjun Kumar\n| [[Balaji Mohan]]\n|Tamil\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Padaiveeran]]''\n| Munishwaran\n| Dhana\n|Tamil\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of Indian playback singers]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Vijay Yesudas}}\n* [http://www.vijayyesudas.com Official Website of Vijay Yesudas]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20131202222927/http://malayalasangeetham.info/displayProfile.php?category=singers&artist=Vijay%20Yesudas Complete Analysis of Vijay Yesudas' malayalam career from MSI/MMDb Encyclopedia]\n* {{IMDb name|1320481}}\n* [http://www.hinduonnet.com/2007/01/22/stories/2007012221820300.htm Star-lit Wedding for Vijay Yesudas]\n* Chronological listing of film songs sung by Vijay Yesudas in [http://www.raaga.com/channels/tamil/artist/Vijay_Yesudas.html Tamil], [http://www.raaga.com/channels/malayalam/artist/Vijay_Yesudas.html Malayalam] and [http://www.raaga.com/channels/kannada/artist/Vijay_Yesudas.html Kannada language], categorised by song title\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vijay Yesudas}}\n[[Category:Bollywood playback singers]]\n[[Category:Telugu playback singers]]\n[[Category:Malayalam playback singers]]\n[[Category:Indian male film singers]]\n[[Category:Singers from Kochi]]\n