ina vs Chile|Match 1}}\n|team2      = {{fb|CHI}}\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    = [[Estadio Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti|Estadio Monumental]], [[Buenos Aires]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|report     =\n}}<section end=A01 />\n\n====Australia vs Uruguay====\n<section begin=A02 />{{Football box\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|6|13|df=y}}\n|time       = 16:00 <includeonly>[[Time in Argentina|ART]]</includeonly>\n|team1      = {{fb-rt|AUS}}\n|score      = {{score link|2021 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group A#Australia vs Uruguay|Match 3}}\n|team2      = {{fb|URU}}\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    = [[Estadio Mario Alberto Kempes]], [[C\u00f3rdoba, Argentina|C\u00f3rdoba]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|report     =\n}}<section end=A02 />\n\n====Paraguay vs Bolivia====\n<section begin=A03 />{{Football box\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|6|13|df=y}}\n|time       = 19:00 <includeonly>[[Time in Argentina|ART]]</includeonly>\n|team1      = {{fb-rt|PAR}}\n|score      = {{score link|2021 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group A#Paraguay vs Bolivia|Match 4}}\n|team2      = {{fb|BOL}}\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    = [[Estadio Malvinas Argentinas]], [[Mendoza, Argentina|Mendoza]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|report     =\n}}<section end=A03 />\n\n===Matchday 2===\n\n====Chile vs Bolivia====\n<section begin=A04 />{{Football box\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|6|16|df=y}}\n|time       = 19:00 <includeonly>[[Time in Argentina|ART]]</includeonly>\n|team1      = {{fb-rt|CHI}}\n|score      = {{score link|2021 Copa Am\u00e9rica Group A#Chile vs Bolivia|Match 8}}\n|team2      = {{fb|BOL}}\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    = [[Estadio Malvinas Argentinas]], [[Mendoza, Argentina|Mendoza]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|report     =\n}}<section end=A04 />\n\n====Argentina vs Uruguay====\n<section begin=A05 />{{Football box\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|6|16|df=y}}\n|time       = 22:00 <includeonly>[[Time in Argentina|ART]]</includeonly>\n|team1      =